; Reverses the value at 0x3050 into 0x3051.
; CSC 225, Assignment 2
; Given code, Winter '24

0011 0000 0000 0000     ; Start at 0x3000.

                        ; R0 = Bit we are reversing
                        ; R1 = Result
                        ; R2 = #1

0101 001 001 100000     ; And R1 with 0 to clear
0010 010 000 001000     ; Load R2 to #1
0010 000 001 001101     ; Load R0 to 0x3050

0000 011 000 000 001    ; If Negative
0001 001 010 000 001    ; Combine R2 and R1 to R1

0001 010 010 000010     ; Rotate R2
0001 000 000 000000     ; Rotate R0
0000 101 111 111011     ; Restart Loop if bit we are reversing is not 0

0011 001 001 001000     ; Store at 0x3051
1111 0000 00100101      ; Halt

0000 0000 0000 0001     ; #1
